# font selection

[Nerd Fonts - Iconic font aggregator, glyphs/icons collection, & fonts patcher](https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads)
[Programming Fonts - Test Drive](https://www.programmingfonts.org/#jetbrainsmono)


# font installation

## install font package
% yay -Sy $font_package

## update font database
% fc-cache --force --verbose

## verify available fonts
% fc-list | grep $font

## change font in application configs, e.g.:
alacritty
emacs
sway
tofi
